replies.body:
Two things that I would like to see happen to the bug;

1: Riot used math incorrectly for the isolation changes. The radius increase to 500 from 350 was a 42.8% increase. However, **isolation is an area**. A range increase of 42.8% increases the area by 104%. That's ludicrous. If Riot wanted to increase isolation by 42.8%, then the radius would be approximately 418.33 units. I would be fine with an isolation radius anywhere from 400-425 (rounding for simplicity). 


2: Kha's ultimate re-stealth still takes 2 seconds. Riot increased it to two from one because they didn't want Kha to have 50% damage reduction for 6 seconds. After they removed the damage reduction from Evo'd ult, **they did not revert the re-stealth time. There is literally no reason why this has not been reverted.**
